### Retrieve all users with optional pagination (GET)
GET https://api.example.com/v1/users?page=1&limit=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Retrieve a single user by ID (GET)
GET https://api.example.com/v1/users/42
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new user (POST)
POST https://api.example.com/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Elena Ruiz",
  "email": "elena.ruiz@example.com",
  "role": "editor"
}

###

### Update an existing user (PUT)
PUT https://api.example.com/v1/users/42
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Elena R. Ruiz",
  "email": "elena.ruiz@example.com",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Delete a user (DELETE)
DELETE https://api.example.com/v1/users/42
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
